        "id": 20190109,
        "subfield": "Trigonometry",
        "context": "2019年全国高中数学联合竞赛A卷解答题",
        "question": "在 $\\triangle ABC$ 中，$BC = a, CA = b, AB = c$。若 $b$ 是 $a$ 与 $c$ 的等比中项，且 $\\sin A$ 是 $\\sin(B-A)$ 与 $\\sin C$ 的等差中项，求 $\\cos B$ 的值。",
        "solution": [
            "罗列条件 $b^{2} = ac$",
            "$2\\sin A = \\sin(B-A) + \\sin C = \\sin(B-A) + \\sin(B+A) = 2\\sin B\\cos A$",
            "$\\cos A = \\frac{a}{b} = \\frac{b^{2} + c^{2} - a^{2}}{2ac}$",
            "即 $2ac = b^{2} + c^{2} - a^{2}$，由 $b^{2} = ac$ 可得 $c^{2} - ca - a^{2} = 0$",
            "于是 $\\frac{c}{a} = \\frac{\\sqrt{5}+1}{2}$",
            "于是 $b^{2} = \\frac{\\sqrt{5}+1}{2}a^{2}$，$c^{2} = \\frac{3+\\sqrt{5}}{2}a^{2}$",
            "解得 $\\cos B = \\frac{a^{2} + c^{2} - b^{2}}{2ac} = \\frac{\\sqrt{5}-1}{2}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{\\sqrt{5}-1}{2}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
