        "id": 20190111,
        "subfield": "Complex Numbers",
        "context": "2019年全国高中数学联合竞赛A卷解答题",
        "question": "称一个复数列 $\\{z_{n}\\}$ 是"有趣的"，若 $|z_{1}| = 1$，且对任意正整数 $n$，均有 $4z_{n+1}^{2} + 2z_{n}z_{n+1} + z_{n}^{2} = 0$。求最大的常数 $C$，使得对一切有趣的数列 $\\{z_{n}\\}$ 及任意正整数 $m$，均有 $|z_{1} + z_{2} + \\dots + z_{m}| \\geq C$。",
        "solution": [
            "根据题意，有 $z_{n+1} = \\frac{-1\\pm\\sqrt{3}\\mathrm{i}}{4}z_{n} \\iff z_{n+1} = (\\pm\\frac{2\\pi}{3}: \\frac{1}{2}) \\cdot z_{n}$",
            "记 $q_{1} = (\\frac{2\\pi}{3}: \\frac{1}{2})$，$q_{2} = (-\\frac{2\\pi}{3}: \\frac{1}{2})$",
            "取 $z_{1} = 1$，且 $z_{n+1} = \\begin{cases} q_{1}\\cdot z_{n}, & 2\\nmid n \\\\ q_{2}\\cdot z_{n}, & 2\\mid n \\end{cases}$",
            "则 $\\lim_{m\\to+\\infty}(z_{1}+z_{2}+\\cdots+z_{m}) = (0:1) + (\\frac{2\\pi}{3}:\\frac{2}{3}) + (-\\frac{2\\pi}{3}:\\frac{1}{3}) = \\frac{1}{2} + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{6}\\mathrm{i}$",
            "因此 $\\lim_{m\\to+\\infty}|z_{1}+z_{2}+\\dots+z_{m}| = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$",
            "接下来证明 $C = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$ 符合题意",
            "考虑 $|z_{n} + z_{n+1}| = |z_{n}| \\cdot |1 + \\frac{z_{n+1}}{z_{n}}| = \\frac{1}{2^{n-1}} \\cdot |1 + (\\pm\\frac{2\\pi}{3}:\\frac{1}{2})| = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2^{n}}$",
            "于是当 $m = 1$ 时，有 $|z_{1}| = 1 > \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$",
            "当 $m$ 为偶数时，有 $|z_{1}+z_{2}+\\cdots+z_{m}| \\geq |z_{1}+z_{2}| - |z_{3}+z_{4}| - \\cdots - |z_{m-1}+z_{m}| > \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} - (\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{8} + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{32} + \\cdots) = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$",
            "当 $m$ 为不小于3的奇数时，有 $|z_{1}+z_{2}+\\cdots+z_{m}| \\geq |z_{1}+z_{2}| - |z_{3}+z_{4}| - \\cdots - |z_{m-2}+z_{m-1}| - |z_{m}| > \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$",
            "综上所述，符合题意的最大常数为 $\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{3}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
